{"tid":2322373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國2020年向世界各地出售2000億個口罩，成全球最大口罩出口國","createTime":"2020-12-12T09:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T12:15:20.000Z","uid":98317,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"95f5ee181d12b1f4984f534c7153a105804ab545","tid":2322373,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:31:27.000Z","msg":"王毅：中國已向各國提供了2000多億個口罩<br />\n<br />\n11日，王毅談2020中國外交時表示，中國向150多個國家和9個國際組織提供抗疫援助，為有需要的34個國家派出36支醫療專家組。發揮最大醫療物資產能國優勢，迄今已向各國提供了2000多億個口罩、20億件防護服、8億份檢測試劑盒，共中美國更是中國最大買家，己向中國購買近972億個口罩"},{"pid":"e2e101e77e568b3347a0cb4d7ea10485edb0e2cb","tid":2322373,"uid":60924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"3M做完送去美國都計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828b1c788dc501b5b1a0434304501ac5ccec6ffe","tid":2322373,"uid":51200,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"提供了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfor free?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3093e6c0b7ae1064f1ad3eb7586c29456e31d957","tid":2322373,"uid":4964,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"828b1c788dc501b5b1a0434304501ac5ccec6ffe","tid":2322373,"uid":51200,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"提供了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfor free?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"佢買你嘢又要感謝佢<br />\n佢賣你嘢都要感謝佢<br />\n贏國又贏"},{"pid":"2fec268e3efae2792e585f78abf951e2327417a0","tid":2322373,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:10:42.000Z","msg":"退貨數字呢？"},{"pid":"9f86bbbe9fbfa36b059084654cc7